{"tid":1134880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"芳香撲鼻！為食大媽踎超市　即場歎榴槤夠晒新鮮？","createTime":"2019-05-02T03:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T03:27:25.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b44f8452ed9412be5ea416961ac6ab80ff257b63","tid":1134880,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>芳香撲鼻！為食大媽踎超市 即場歎榴槤夠晒新鮮？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PDRfLB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PDRfLB&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=42c3cffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PDRfLB</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502103534518-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190502111329\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502103534518-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190502111329&h=e849d7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網民周一（29日）上傳相片至Facebook群組「To Kwa Wan 土瓜灣之友」，只見在一間超級市場的收銀處旁，有3名女子圍蹲在店內大吃榴槤，其中一名大媽更懶理玉背大露，吃得津津有味。<br />\n<br />\n剛巧，上周六有同區街坊在另一間超市分店門外，亦見到兩名女子坐在大街上，共享榴槤。該街坊亦不禁嘲笑道︰「好好味咁喎」。"},{"pid":"ade1681cb47431ecf0a827fc7a2015d330f30773","tid":1134880,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a023542d6775ea162480e8760de87dcc063d7b7","tid":1134880,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"係度食, 係度...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08504770012e4d43fd51a90ffd55484c9301e6fd","tid":1134880,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"馬總統看手錶"}]}